<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Chọn Vai Trò - Viroom.com</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #6a82fb, #fc5c7d);
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            color: white;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .role-option {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2rem 3rem;
            margin: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

            .role-option:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
                box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            }

            .role-option h2 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

            .role-option p {
                margin-top: 0.5rem;
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            /* Gradient colors from the new image */
            .role-option.student {
                background: linear-gradient(45deg, #a1c4fd, #c2e9fb);
                color: #333;
            }

            .role-option.teacher {
                background: linear-gradient(45deg, #fbc2eb, #a6c1ee);
                color: #333;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-white">Bạn là ai?</h1>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center">
            <a href="/Account/Register?role=student" class="role-option student rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <h2>Học sinh</h2>
                <p>Tôi là một học sinh, đang tìm kiếm một lớp học.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/Account/Register?role=teacher" class="role-option teacher rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <h2>Giáo viên</h2>
                <p>Tôi là một giáo viên, muốn quản lý lớp học của mình.</p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
